12:53:42  54            **          Called by: PKG_COMPANY_TRADE.p_get_monthly_dbt_trend, PKG_COMPANY_SUMMARY.get_dashboard
12:53:42  55            **          Author: Bartlomiej Sus / SMT
12:53:42  56            **          Date:   2012-09-26
